  <!-- EN: bliss -->
  <VPE_Bliss.label>極樂</VPE_Bliss.label>
  <!-- EN: After a brief meditation period, induce a sense of serenity in the target that reaches maximum magnitude near the effect’s end. As the calming feeling becomes more pronounced, they will find it harder to concentrate but it is not considered a malicious action. -->
  <VPE_Bliss.description>短暫的冥想後，在目標腦中生成一股逐漸增強的快感。效果越是增強，目標越會感到自己意識模糊，難以集中，但這並不被視作敵意舉動。</VPE_Bliss.description>
  <!-- EN: Using ability: {0} -->
  <VPE_Bliss.jobReportString>使用能力：{0}</VPE_Bliss.jobReportString>
  <!-- EN: 極樂 -->
  <VPE_Bliss.verbProperties.label>極樂</VPE_Bliss.verbProperties.label>
  
  <!-- EN: energy dump -->
  <VPE_EnergyDump.label>體能轉移</VPE_EnergyDump.label>
  <!-- EN: Purges the build-up of fatigue in a nearby target and leaves them completely refreshed, in exchange the caster is left completely exhausted and needing a good nap. -->
  <VPE_EnergyDump.description>將目標的所有疲勞清除，而施放者則會立刻精疲力竭。</VPE_EnergyDump.description>
  <!-- EN: Using ability: {0} -->
  <VPE_EnergyDump.jobReportString>使用能力：{0}</VPE_EnergyDump.jobReportString>
  <!-- EN: 體能轉移 -->
  <VPE_EnergyDump.verbProperties.label>體能轉移</VPE_EnergyDump.verbProperties.label>
  
  <!-- EN: mind wipe -->
  <VPE_MindWipe.label>洗腦</VPE_MindWipe.label>
  <!-- EN: Induce a harmless, instantaneous retrograde amnesia in the target, purging all memories, social bonds and skills acquired outside of their backstory. They also feel a strong kinship with the caster’s colony and joy at rediscovering the joys of life without commitment. -->
  <VPE_MindWipe.description>用一種無害的逆心靈脈衝使目標失憶，洗去所有記憶，社會關係並使技能回歸他們背景故事決定的基礎值。並創造出對殖民地的歸屬感，使其有欲望重新開始一切。</VPE_MindWipe.description>
  <!-- EN: Using ability: {0} -->
  <VPE_MindWipe.jobReportString>使用能力：{0}</VPE_MindWipe.jobReportString>
  <!-- EN: 洗腦 -->
  <VPE_MindWipe.verbProperties.label>洗腦</VPE_MindWipe.verbProperties.label>
  
  <!-- EN: reunion farskip -->
  <VPE_ReunionFarskip.label>血脈折躍</VPE_ReunionFarskip.label>
  <!-- EN: After a short meditation period and followed by a 5-day coma, taps into a target’s bloodline to skip all living family members to their proximity, knocked out through psychic shock. However, it does nothing to change their relationships and is considered rude by all other factions. -->
  <VPE_ReunionFarskip.description>短暫的冥想後，施放者將進入五天的精神昏迷。追朔目標的血緣，將所有在該星球上的親人折躍到附近，折躍過來的人會在心靈能力的衝擊中陷入昏迷。此能力並不會改變被折躍者的社交關係和派系歸屬，而且會激怒所有的派系。</VPE_ReunionFarskip.description>
  <!-- EN: Using ability: {0} -->
  <VPE_ReunionFarskip.jobReportString>使用能力：{0}</VPE_ReunionFarskip.jobReportString>
  <!-- EN: 血脈折躍 -->
  <VPE_ReunionFarskip.verbProperties.label>血脈折躍</VPE_ReunionFarskip.verbProperties.label>
  
